original_title: WWE Tagged Classics: Austin 3:16 Uncensored / Three Faces Of Foley / Chris Jericho: Break Down The Walls / Kurt Angle: Its True
overview: Collection of programmes that celebrate the career and greatest fights of some of WWE's most iconic figures. 'Austin 3:16 Uncensored' takes a look at the history of 'Stone Cold' Steve Austin, who was inducted into the WWE Hall of Fame in 2009. 'Three Faces of Foley' looks at the lengthy WWE career of Mick Foley, who also fought under the pseudonyms Mankind, Dude Love and Cactus Jack. 'Chris Jericho - Break Down the Walls' celebrates the performer's decade in WWE and 'Kurt Angle - It's True' pays tribute to Kurt Angle, an Olympic wrestling gold medallist as well as a star WWE performer.
